summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of One Hundred Thirteen and 44/100 ($113.44) Dollars, from Local Improvement District No. 1861 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said District, for the improvement of Sixth Avenue Northeast and other streets, and avenues, all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 19421.
